Often, you\[aq]ll want to see just one line per interval.
The \f[C]\-\-depth\f[] option helps with this, causing subaccounts to be
aggregated:
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
$\ hledger\ register\ \-\-monthly\ assets\ \-\-depth\ 1h
2008/01\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ assets\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $1
2008/06\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ assets\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ $\-1\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ 0
