especially if your bank supports OFX download.
.SS diff
.PP
Show transactions present in one journal file but not another
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
$\ hledger\ diff\ \-\-help
Usage:\ hledger\-diff\ account:name\ left.journal\ right.journal
